DOC.brief_summary: A retrospective study to evaluate healthcare cost and resource utilization for patients with metastatic renal cell carcinoma who have been treated with IV or oral agents
DOC.brief_title: Healthcare Cost and Resource Utilization Related to Metastatic Renal Cell Carcinoma Treatment With Intravenous and Oral Agents
DOC.criteria: Diagnosis with metastatic renal cell carcinoma Prescription/administration of one of the IV or oral agents examined in the study Patients with other primary cancer diagnosis before RCC diagnosis Patients with pregnancy or HIV/AIDS
